metadata.name: The Moment : The only two anonymous.
metadata.description:
The artwork is created and formatted in high resolution digital art form. The outbreak of the pandemic is making changes everywhere to anyone. Plates and mugs sit on the tables of an empty restaurant, serving the only two anonymous.Silence and emptiness quarantined the two anonymous in the parallel universe.
